{"type":null,"faqId":33664,"title":"搜狐视频亮度突然变亮，播放结束后又变暗","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">启动搜狐视频后，在播放界面，按返回键退出，界面的背光先一下子变亮，然后再慢慢恢复正常。由于观看视频过程中，视频类应用自身以可调节系统屏幕的亮度，并且比手机系统正常标准更亮，以保证观看效果。当退出视频后，系统根据环境光线恢复正常亮度，以节约手机电量。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8384","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748688000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"搜狐视频,亮度","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}